OL,4,CUK's furlough scheme starts to wind
OL,5,Cdown
OL,6, Employers will have to shoulder more of
OL,7, the costs of furlough from Thursday as
OL,8, the government starts to wind down its
OL,9, flagship job support scheme.
OL,11,FWith about 1.5 million workers still on
OL,12,Ffurlough, the change will affect
OL,13,Fthousands of firms across the country.
OL,15,FStaff will continue to receive 80% of
OL,16,Ftheir wages, but employers will pay
OL,17,Fpart of that for the first time.
OL,19,FThat could prompt layoffs, with older
OL,20,Fworkers at greater risk of redundancy,
OL,21,Faccording to one think tank.
